{"tid":1086902,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"正常香港人邊可能食得夠膳食纖維?","createTime":"2019-04-01T05:01:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-03T11:50:58.000Z","uid":29880,"like":15,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"8cea06985b30406951befba960a930944c393ebd","tid":1086902,"uid":29880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T05:01:39.000Z","msg":"世衛建議每日最少攝取25g膳食纖維<br />\n即係平均每餐8g左右<br />\n100g菜心先得嗰1.5g纖維<br />\n生菜嗰啲更少<br />\n平均每餐最少要食成斤菜先夠<br />\n生果一個平均都係得2-3g<br />\n出街食早午餐幾乎唔會有菜<br />\n香港又唔興食紅米,糙米<br />\n正常香港人邊可能食得夠膳食纖維?"},{"pid":"eee8948d66c44e0137d504245487a89b3b440424","tid":1086902,"uid":202412,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T05:04:32.000Z","msg":"100g 西蘭花有5.5g<br />\n100g 麥皮有over 10g<br />\n少啲出街食 其實唔難<br />\n<br />\nBTW嗰個係建議 食少幾日唔會有大問題"},{"pid":"38e44b88c6ec9c52b97c2668abff417db1474154","tid":1086902,"uid":29880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eee8948d66c44e0137d504245487a89b3b440424","tid":1086902,"uid":202412,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T05:04:32.000Z","msg":"100g 西蘭花有5.5g<br />\n100g 麥皮有over 10g<br />\n少啲出街食 其實唔難<br />\n<br />\nBTW嗰個係建議 食少幾日唔會有大問題"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T05:09:11.000Z","msg":"邊款麥皮有10g<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n介紹俾我"},{"pid":"de938b9d89899346ded74c68cd1030280aaf20cf","tid":1086902,"uid":202412,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"38e44b88c6ec9c52b97c2668abff417db1474154","tid":1086902,"uid":29880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eee8948d66c44e0137d504245487a89b3b440424","tid":1086902,"uid":202412,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T05:04:32.000Z","msg":"100g 西蘭花有5.5g<br />\n100g 麥皮有over 10g<br />\n少啲出街食 其實唔難<br />\n<br />\nBTW嗰個係建議 食少幾日唔會有大問題"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T05:09:11.000Z","msg":"邊款麥皮有10g<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n介紹俾我"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-0